Chidinma Leilani Aaron (amụrụ na 16 Eprel 1993) bụ onye Naijirịa, onye ọchụnta ego, onye isi nri, onye njikwa mmepe azụmaahịa na ọkà okwu na-akpali akpali.
A mụrụ Chidinma na Kaduna, Kaduna State ma zụlite ya na Federal Capital Territory, Abuja, Niajirịa
Ọ bụ otu n'ime ụmụnne nwanyị atọ na otu nwanne nwoke
O mechara kwaga Ibadan, Oyo State wee gaa Mahadum Lead City, ebe ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ na nzere bachelọ nke sayensị na Business Administration na 2017.
Tupu ọ merie Miss Nigeria, ọ rụrụ ọrụ dị ka onye isi nri na onye njikwa mmekọrịta ndị ahịa na Yumme Meals, ụlọ nri na ihe oriri dị na F.C.T., Abuja.
